BT /F1 10 Tf 54 464 Td (The AI-Enhanced CRM & Ticket Management System is a web-based support platform inspired) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 450 Td (by Zendesk and Freshdesk. It allows support agents and managers to manage customer) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 436 Td (records, create and track support tickets, maintain ticket communication history, view) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 422 Td (dashboards, use Gemini AI for support workflows, and send Telegram notifications for) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 408 Td (important events.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 388 Td (The project satisfies the assignment requirements by providing persistent storage,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 374 Td (secure authentication, role-based access control, customer management, ticket) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 360 Td (management, activity logs, dashboards, real AI features, and real messaging integration.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 346 Td (The application is intentionally built with a simple university-project stack: FastAPI,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 332 Td (SQLite, SQLAlchemy, HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript. This keeps the project easy to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 318 Td (run, inspect, explain in viva, and extend.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 298 Td (The final demo should be recorded with real Gemini and Telegram keys configured.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 284 Td (Development fallback mode is included only so the system remains usable when secrets are) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 270 Td (not available.) Tj ET
BT /F1 13 Tf 54 250 Td (3. Project Objectives) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 224 Td (The main objectives were:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 204 Td (- Build a mini CRM where managers and agents can log in securely.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 190 Td (- Allow managers to manage customer data and agent accounts.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 176 Td (- Allow tickets to be created, assigned, filtered, updated, resolved, and closed.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 162 Td (- Maintain a full ticket timeline containing comments, status changes, priority changes,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 148 Td (assignments, AI actions, and notifications.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 134 Td (- Show customer profile pages with full ticket and communication history.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 120 Td (- Use Google Gemini inside real workflows, not as a separate toy feature.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 106 Td (- Send Telegram messages to a real account/channel and persist delivery logs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 92 Td (- Provide a dashboard and reports for managerial decision-making.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 78 Td (- Keep the application simple enough to be presented and defended in a student viva.) Tj ET
